cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper focuses on deep reinforcement learning for robotic object manipulation problems, which involves both machine learning and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the use of curriculum learning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves computer vision techniques for object recognition, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper discusses the use of hindsight experience replay, which is a technique used in control systems, falling under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control).
